@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.57 * v1 + 0.36) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.49)) * wp.exp((tmp + 0.22 * v0 + 0.87)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp))
    v2 = wp.abs((0.71 * v1))
    data[tid] = v0
